        <abstract> 
<p>Sends CD a statement of number of thousands of copies printed thus far [by Murray’s] of: <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi> (12), <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> (13), <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> (10), and <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi> (9).</p> 
        </abstract>
